ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would highly recommend this class.
I would recommend the course for a fellow student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This class was instrumental in deepening my knowledge in my field. It helped me integrate my tool kit as an artist and an academic.The readings were extremely helpful for my project. Specifically, looking at geography, space, aesthetic, affect, structure of feeling and everydayness and racist practices.My writing also greatly improved.
